Yard and pool service is included. 12 months minimum term preferred. Good credit, verifiable income, and renters insurance required.

description:
At the blue Pacific Ocean's edge and elevated one story above the sand at Kaimana Beach, this spacious studio could be your pied-à-terre home away from home. Sans Souci epitomizes its definition, “without worry”, as one of many secure residential buildings defining Honolulu's Gold Coast — to Hawaiians past, kapua, “the flower”. Swaying palms will inspire you by day as waves lull you to peaceful sleep each night. Choose to sleep on its lanai, large enough to function as a bedroom and furnished with a comfy wall bed, or opt for the interior sofa sleeper. Electric lanai shades allow you to control light and weather patterns.
Sans Souci offers you unparalleled access to healthy living - swim, snorkel, dive, kayak, hike, bike, yoga, lots of eateries from casual to fine dining like the Hau Tree restaurant and Michels restaurant; short distances to shopping galore; personal services and medical care; groceries and farmer's markets; Outrigger Canoe Club and Elk's Lodge are next door.
Available June 1, 2024. Prefer a 6 month min. lease.
Security deposit is equal to one month's rent.
Application Fee: $45.
Utilities included: Electricity, Sewer, Water, Hot Water, Parking.
